COD4 is so amazing though. <br><BR><font size=1>05:07 12-14-2007</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' bgcolor=#CCCCCC>&nbsp;</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#CCCCCC><font class="bfont"><B>Patrick M. S</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#CCCCCC' ><font class="bfont">ahhhhhhh, you fockers playing Gears without me!? :(<br />
